OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FThe US expanded its airstrike campaign
OL,7,Fagainst Iran early on Friday by
OL,8,Fhitting more bridges and collapsing a
OL,9,Ftower at a key Iranian port.
OL,11,FIt follows US President Donald Trump's
OL,12,Fthreats to start striking
OL,13,Finfrastructure to pressure Tehran to
OL,14,Fease its chokehold on the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz.
OL,17,FIran launched retaliatory missile
OL,18,Fattacks against US-allied nations in
OL,19,Fthe Middle East, including Qatar, a
OL,20,Fkey mediator in the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
