PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784445485
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FWhen the US and Israel launched the
OL,7,Fwar on Iran on February 28, Tehran
OL,8,Feffectively closed the strait to
OL,9,Fshipping traffic, a move that sent the
OL,10,Fprice of oil soaring and gave Iran
OL,11,Fmajor leverage in negotiations.
OL,13,FSpeaking in a primetime address to the
OL,14,FAmerican public, Trump insisted the
OL,15,Fwar was going well.
OL,17,F"We are likewise winning big in Iran,
OL,18,Fand you will see the fruits of that
OL,19,Flabor very, very shortly," Trump said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
