OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSeven people were killed when the US
OL,12,Fstruck bridges in Iran's southern
OL,13,FHormozgan province overnight into
OL,14,FFriday, Iranian state television
OL,15,Freported. The attacks hit Bandar
OL,16,FKhamir, a city on Iran's coast on the
OL,17,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
