PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784445485
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FThe US military's Central Command said
OL,7,Fit hit dozens of targets in its latest
OL,8,Fairstrikes, which concluded at dawn
OL,9,FFriday, the sixth night in a row of
OL,10,FAmerican attacks.
OL,12,FThe strikes also collapsed a tower at
OL,13,FIran's Chabahar port on the Gulf of
OL,14,FOman, a key trade route for
OL,15,Flandlocked, neighboring Afghanistan,
OL,16,Fthe state-run IRNA news agency
OL,17,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
