PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784445485
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FUS Defense Secretary Pete Hegseth
OL,7,Fshared the image of the surveillance
OL,8,Ftower collapsing, part of his effort
OL,9,Fto assert American control over the
OL,10,Fstrait. That image had circulated
OL,11,Fsocial media via activists prior to
OL,12,FHegseth sharing it.
OL,14,FChabahar port, which Iran had been
OL,15,Frunning with support from India, has
OL,16,Fbeen a repeated target of American
OL,17,Fairstrikes. Iranian state media
OL,18,Facknowledged a third round of strikes
OL,19,Fon the facility without immediately
OL,20,Facknowledging the tower's collapse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
