OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784445485
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FIran described the tower as overseeing
OL,7,Fcommercial traffic into the port.
OL,8,FHowever, Iran's paramilitary
OL,9,FRevolutionary Guard also operates at
OL,10,Fports across the country.
OL,12,FOn Friday, Qatar twice warned the
OL,13,Fpublic to take shelter as a barrage of
OL,14,FIranian missiles targeted the nation.
OL,15,FPeople heard explosions overhead as
OL,16,Fair defenses fired to intercept the
OL,17,Fmissiles. Qatar's Interior Ministry
OL,18,Fsaid falling debris wounded a child.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
