PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784445485
OL,3,CUS strikes Iran for sixth night,
OL,4,Cbringing down bridges and a tower
OL,6,FQatar is a key mediator with Pakistan
OL,7,Fin trying to reach an end to the Iran
OL,8,Fwar. But talks have broken down over
OL,9,FIran's chokehold on the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz.
OL,12,FIran also targeted Bahrain and Kuwait
OL,13,Fearly Friday.
OL,15,FExplosions also could be heard Friday
OL,16,Fmorning in Irbil and Sulaymaniyah in
OL,17,Fnorthern Iraq's semiautonomous Kurdish
OL,18,Fregion as air defenses targeted
OL,19,Fincoming fire. There was no immediate
OL,20,Fword on any damage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
